title: A5 Silent Non-Ticking Bedside Alarm Clock, 4" Metal Structure, Retro Vintage Design with Twin Bell, Perfect for Heavy Sleepers, Kids and Bedrooms. Analogue Quartz and Battery Operated. (BLUE DIAL)
features: [Full Metal Solid Structure] This Retro Twin Bell Alarm Clock is made with all metal premium solid structure, wtih silkscreen glass cover and aluminium dial, featuring premium taste and retro traditional design which is unlike other alarm clocks found in common market.

[Extra Loud Alarm] Twin bell alarm systm featuring extra loud alarm sound, which is perfect for people whio are heavy sleeps, mild loss hearing even deaf. Without a snooze button which made it a ghood wake up clock for people who has trouble waking up.

[Noiseless and Quiet] Our Retro Twin Bell Alarm Clock using premium quality smooth sweep movement, featuring silent sweep second-hand, absolutely silent, without any annoying ticking, which provides quiet sleeping and working environment.

[Classic Retro Vintage Design] This vintage twin bell alarm clock with retro style takes you back to the 80's. Its beautiful and shinny look, with premium quality workmanship. This retro designed alarm clock can be placed on the desktop, livingroom or in the bedroom. It is also a very nice handmade decoration.

[Easy to Operate] Compare to modern digital alarm clocks, our alarm clocks just have four buttons: Two dials to set clock and alarm, one alarm switch to turn on/off alarm and the NIGHTLIGHT button for time watching in dark. Nightlight feature makes the clock easy to read in the night. And it is operated by 2 piece of AA battery which is NOT INCLUDED IN THE PACKAGE. (NOTE: All Analog Clocks MUST USE 1.5V AA CARBON BATTERIES)

[OUR WARRANTY] We are confident in our quality products, thats why we offer unconditionally refund or free replace if defective or any quality problems within first year, plus life-time friendly customer service.
